      <title>阿布達比人工智慧公司 Presight 獲得科技企業 AIQ 多數股權</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/abu-dhabi-ai-company-presight-takes-majority-stake-tech-venture-aiq-2024-05-01/</link>
